        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","imitate - 模仿，仿效，仿制","Children often imitate their parents' behavior. 孩子经常模仿父母的行为。\n搭配: imitate the style 模仿风格\n同义词: copy, mimic","v. imitates, imitating, imitated","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","immense - 巨大的，广大的","The project requires immense resources. 该项目需要巨大的资源。\n搭配: immense pressure 巨大压力\n同义词: enormous, vast","adj. immensely (adv.)","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","immigrate - 移民，移入","Many people immigrate to America for better opportunities. 许多人为了更好的机会移民到美国。\n搭配: immigrate to 移民到\n同义词: migrate, relocate","v. immigrates, immigrating, immigrated","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","impact - 影响，冲击，碰撞","Technology has had a huge impact on education. 技术对教育产生了巨大影响。\n搭配: have an impact on 对...有影响\n同义词: effect, influence","n./v. impacts, impacting, impacted","Easy"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","imply - 暗示，意味着，含有...的意思","His silence implied agreement. 他的沉默暗示了同意。\n搭配: imply that 暗示\n同义词: suggest, indicate","v. implies, implying, implied","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","impose - 强加，征收，利用","The government imposed new taxes on imports. 政府对进口商品征收新税。\n搭配: impose on 强加于\n同义词: force, levy","v. imposes, imposing, imposed","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","incentive - 激励，刺激，动力","Tax incentives encourage investment. 税收优惠鼓励投资。\n搭配: financial incentive 财政激励\n同义词: motivation, stimulus","n. incentives","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","incident - 事件，事变，插曲","The incident was reported in the news. 该事件在新闻中被报道。\n搭配: incident report 事件报告\n同义词: event, occurrence","n. incidents","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","incline - 倾斜，倾向于，易于","I'm inclined to agree with your opinion. 我倾向于同意你的观点。\n搭配: be inclined to 倾向于\n同义词: tend, lean","v./n. inclines, inclining, inclined","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","incorporate - 包含，合并，组成公司","The new design incorporates the latest technology. 新设计融合了最新技术。\n搭配: incorporate into 合并到\n同义词: include, integrate","v. incorporates, incorporating, incorporated","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","index - 索引，指数，指标","The consumer price index rose by 2%. 消费者物价指数上涨了2%。\n搭配: price index 价格指数\n同义词: indicator, guide","n./v. indexes, indexing, indexed","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","indicate - 表明，指示，暗示","Research indicates that exercise improves mental health. 研究表明运动能改善心理健康。\n搭配: indicate that 表明\n同义词: show, suggest","v. indicates, indicating, indicated","Easy"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","indispensable - 必不可少的，不可或缺的","Water is indispensable for survival. 水对生存是必不可少的。\n搭配: be indispensable to 对...不可或缺\n同义词: essential, vital","adj. indispensably (adv.)","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","induce - 诱导，引起，导致","The drug can induce sleep. 这种药能引起睡眠。\n搭配: induce sb. to do sth. 诱使某人做某事\n同义词: cause, persuade","v. induces, inducing, induced","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","inevitable - 不可避免的，必然的","Change is inevitable in life. 变化在生活中是不可避免的。\n搭配: inevitable result 必然结果\n同义词: unavoidable, certain","adj. inevitably (adv.)","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","infect - 感染，传染","The virus can infect humans. 这种病毒可以感染人类。\n搭配: infect with 感染\n同义词: contaminate, transmit","v. infects, infecting, infected","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","infer - 推断，推论，暗示","From the evidence, we can infer that he is guilty. 从证据中我们可以推断他有罪。\n搭配: infer from 从...推断\n同义词: deduce, conclude","v. infers, inferring, inferred","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","inflation - 通货膨胀，膨胀","Inflation has risen to 5%. 通货膨胀率已升至5%。\n搭配: inflation rate 通货膨胀率\n同义词: price rise, expansion","n. (uncountable)","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","influence - 影响，势力，感化","Parents have a great influence on their children. 父母对孩子有很大影响。\n搭配: have influence on 对...有影响\n同义词: effect, impact","n./v. influences, influencing, influenced","Easy"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","infrastructure - 基础设施，基础建设","The country needs to improve its infrastructure. 该国需要改善基础设施。\n搭配: public infrastructure 公共基础设施\n同义词: foundation, framework","n. (uncountable)","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","inherent - 固有的，内在的，与生俱来的","There are inherent risks in any investment. 任何投资都有固有风险。\n搭配: inherent quality 固有品质\n同义词: innate, built-in","adj. inherently (adv.)","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","inhibit - 抑制，阻止，约束","Fear can inhibit creativity. 恐惧会抑制创造力。\n搭配: inhibit growth 抑制增长\n同义词: restrain, prevent","v. inhibits, inhibiting, inhibited","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","initial - 最初的，开头的，首字母","The initial results are promising. 初步结果很有希望。\n搭配: initial stage 初始阶段\n同义词: first, original","adj./n./v. initials, initialing, initialed","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","initiate - 开始，发起，创始","The company initiated a new training program. 公司启动了新的培训计划。\n搭配: initiate a project 启动项目\n同义词: start, launch","v. initiates, initiating, initiated","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","innovate - 创新，改革","The company continues to innovate in technology. 公司继续在技术方面创新。\n搭配: innovate in 在...方面创新\n同义词: create, pioneer","v. innovates, innovating, innovated","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","insight - 洞察力，深入了解，领悟","The book gives insight into human nature. 这本书深入了解了人性。\n搭配: gain insight into 深入了解\n同义词: understanding, perception","n. insights","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","inspect - 检查，审视，视察","The officer inspected the cargo. 官员检查了货物。\n搭配: inspect for 检查\n同义词: examine, check","v. inspects, inspecting, inspected","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","integrate - 整合，融合，使完整","The school integrates technology into its curriculum. 学校将技术融入课程。\n搭配: integrate into 整合到\n同义词: combine, merge","v. integrates, integrating, integrated","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","integrity - 完整，正直，诚实","He is a man of great integrity. 他是一个非常正直的人。\n搭配: professional integrity 职业操守\n同义词: honesty, wholeness","n. (uncountable)","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","intellectual - 智力的，知识分子，理智的","Reading is an intellectual activity. 阅读是一种智力活动。\n搭配: intellectual property 知识产权\n同义词: mental, academic","adj./n. intellectually (adv.)","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","intense - 强烈的，紧张的，热情的","The competition was intense. 竞争非常激烈。\n搭配: intense pressure 强烈压力\n同义词: extreme, severe","adj. intensely (adv.)","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","interact - 互动，相互作用","Children learn by interacting with others. 孩子通过与他人的互动学习。\n搭配: interact with 与...互动\n同义词: communicate, engage","v. interacts, interacting, interacted","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","interfere - 干涉，妨碍，冲突","Don't interfere in other people's business. 不要干涉别人的事。\n搭配: interfere with 妨碍\n同义词: intervene, meddle","v. interferes, interfering, interfered","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","intermediate - 中间的，中级的","This is an intermediate level course. 这是一门中级课程。\n搭配: intermediate level 中级水平\n同义词: middle, moderate","adj./n./v. intermediates","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","interpret - 解释，翻译，理解","How do you interpret this poem? 你如何解读这首诗？\n搭配: interpret as 解释为\n同义词: explain, translate","v. interprets, interpreting, interpreted","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","intervene - 干预，介入，调停","The government had to intervene in the crisis. 政府不得不干预危机。\n搭配: intervene in 干预\n同义词: interfere, mediate","v. intervenes, intervening, intervened","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","intricate - 复杂的，错综的，难懂的","The watch has an intricate mechanism. 这块手表有复杂的机械装置。\n搭配: intricate design 复杂的设计\n同义词: complex, elaborate","adj. intricately (adv.)","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","intrinsically - 本质上，固有地","Education is intrinsically valuable. 教育本质上是有价值的。\n搭配: intrinsically linked 本质上相关\n同义词: essentially, inherently","adv. (intrinsic adj.)","Hard"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","invest - 投资，投入，授予","The company invested heavily in research. 公司在研究上投入了大量资金。\n搭配: invest in 投资\n同义词: fund, put money into","v. invests, investing, invested","Easy"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","investigate - 调查，研究","The police are investigating the crime. 警方正在调查这起犯罪。\n搭配: investigate the cause 调查原因\n同义词: examine, probe","v. investigates, investigating, investigated","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","isolate - 隔离，孤立，分离","The patient was isolated to prevent infection. 病人被隔离以防止感染。\n搭配: isolate from 与...隔离\n同义词: separate, quarantine","v./adj. isolates, isolating, isolated","Medium"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","issue - 问题，发行，发布","The government issued a statement on the matter. 政府就此事发表了声明。\n搭配: environmental issues 环境问题\n同义词: problem, topic","n./v. issues, issuing, issued","Easy"),
        ("CET-6","Vocabulary","justify - 证明...正当，为...辩护","How can you justify your actions? 你如何为你的行为辩护？\n搭配: justify doing sth. 证明做某事是正当的\n同义词: defend, explain","v. justifies, justifying, justified","Medium"),
